f=Engineering/dana/custom/datastore-selection/assets/helixdb-playbook.md · h1:HelixDB Playbook [business name] 2026-07-09=Dated volatility split (ops/platform-playbooks). HelixDB fast-moving project (first release Feb 2025) VERIFY current features before committing; past staleness horizon playbook flags itself. Source: github.com/helixdb/helix-db, helix-db.com. **As of:** 2026-07-09 **Staleness horizon:** [set months given release velocity] **Source:** github.com/helixdb/helix-db (verify current) · wh:it is=Open-source **graph vector** database, built Rust, OLTP, object storage. AGPL-3.0., Native graph traversal vector search keyword search one engine; supports KV, documents, relational., Query language: **HelixQL** strongly typed, compiled. DSLs Rust, TypeScript, Go, Python; dynamic requests `POST /v1/query`., Positioned "the database memory" RAG pipelines, agent/knowledge apps. · h2:choose (from datastore-selection)=Workload agent memory, RAG-with-relationships, knowledge graphs traversal similarity matter., You'd otherwise bolt vector store onto graph store (or vice versa) maintain seam. · h2:When NOT to=Plain relational/transactional workloads (use relational don't adopt graph-vector CRUD)., relationship similarity need document store simpler operational surface). · h2:toongine memory candidacy (platform ADR dana dev)=HelixDB candidate toongine's graph-memory layer (the blueprint's brain/context/sources)., PLATFORM-level decision, per-business one: decided ADR marcus/board strategic/spend weight applies., adopted platform level, per-business skills read/write "the configured memory layer" they don't hardcode HelixDB. · h2:Operational notes (fill adoption Rail applies data movement)=Deploy/host: <FILL_IN> ops platform-playbook), Backup restore-test: <FILL_IN> ops maintenance-hygiene; restore-tested-or-nonexistent), Schema/migration: HelixQL schema changes migration-discipline scripts dana writes, OPERATOR runs (Rail, Monitoring baselines: <FILL_IN> ops), Egress/connector: <FILL_IN> quinn allowlist, Rail · h2:Verify-before-trust (ground truth beats doc)=\| Date \| Feature/command checked \| Confirmed/corrected \| · h2:Verify-before-trust (ground truth beats doc)=\|---\|---\|---\| · h2:Verify-before-trust (ground truth beats doc)=\| 2026-07-09 \| graph+vector native, HelixQL, POST /v1/query \| per public docs; verify at adoption \|